Emotional AI • In Development

Meet BounceAI, your everyday emotional companion.

Bounce listens, cares, and stays with you through the highs and lows. An AI companion built to support your mood, mindset, and momentum — all in one place.

Built by Tran Thi Hong Duc • Phase 1: IP + Prototype • 2025
Preview
Bounce – Core Character
Status: Private Alpha
ABOUT

Designed for humans who feel deeply.

Bounce isn’t just another chatbot. It’s a soft, expressive AI presence designed to make you feel seen, heard, and supported — especially when life, work, or business feels heavy.

Whether you’re an entrepreneur, creator, athlete, or someone going through a tough time, Bounce aims to be that one gentle presence you can always open your phone and talk to.

Daily emotional check-in Gentle reminders & nudges Non-judgmental listening

The soul of a new ecosystem.

BounceAI is the emotional layer of a larger vision: DEGOIT – a sport & lifestyle ecosystem that blends movement, identity, and technology.

Where DEGOIT trains your body, BounceAI cares for your inner world — helping you stay consistent, confident, and connected.

DEGOIT x Bounce Sport & Mind Long-term vision
FEATURES

What BounceAI can do for you.

  • Send warm, short supportive messages based on your mood.
  • Remind you of your goals when you feel like giving up.
  • Celebrate your small wins and effort, not just results.
  • Stay “present” in your daily routine as a quiet companion.
Mood reflection Micro-encouragement Soft accountability

Planned Modes

  • Calm Mode – for anxiety & overthinking.
  • Focus Mode – short sprints with encouragement.
  • Recovery Mode – when you feel exhausted.
  • Sport Mode – paired with DEGOIT challenges.
Solo user Founder mode Athlete mode
USE CASES

Who is BounceAI for?

Bounce is built for people who carry heavy responsibilities, big dreams, or long-term goals — and need a quiet presence that doesn’t ask for anything back.

  • Entrepreneurs & founders navigating uncertainty and pressure.
  • Young professionals juggling career, family, and identity.
  • Athletes & movers building a stronger body & mind with DEGOIT.
  • Humans in transition – heartbreak, relocation, career change.
ROADMAP

From character to living companion.

BounceAI is in its very early stages — but the arc is clear:

Phase 1 — IP & Visual Character design, protection, and visual system.
Phase 2 — Chat Prototype Emotional chat flows & micro-support scripts.
Phase 3 — App + DEGOIT Integration with movement challenges & identity tracking.
Phase 4 — Ecosystem Marketplace, membership, and global access.
